    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Rank - ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Cargo Haul",
    "DisplayTitle": "Master Rank - Large Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "Hi, \n\nOur client took down a Valakkar and processed it into organics. They've got buyers lined up and waiting for the stuff at a few different locations, so I need someone to go to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>, grab it all, and then deliver it to the following spots:    \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)  \n\nAccording to the manifest, the largest cargo container you\u2019ll need to deal with is <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4>. Don\u2019t forget to bring your <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>. Not sure how you\u2019d move this stuff without it.    \n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)   \n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi, \n\nOur client took down a Valakkar and processed it into organics. They've got buyers lined up and waiting for the stuff at a few different locations, so I need someone to go to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>, grab it all, and then deliver it to the following spots:    \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>Levski</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>Levski</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>Levski</EM4>  \n\nAccording to the manifest, the largest cargo container you\u2019ll need to deal with is <EM4>16 SCU</EM4>. Don\u2019t forget to bring your <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>. Not sure how you\u2019d move this stuff without it.    \n\n[Contractor|SignOff]   \n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
